  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The ratio <math alttext=\"140\"><mn>140</mn>\n</math> to <math alttext=\"m\"><mi>m</mi>\n</math> is equivalent to the ratio <math alttext=\"4\"><mn>4</mn>\n</math> to <math alttext=\"28\"><mn>28</mn>\n</math>. What is the value of <math alttext=\"m\"><mi>m</mi>\n</math>?</p>",
